        "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review-1\n\nHi Satoshi, thanks for submitting this. A few comments before we can go ahead and merge it:\n\n1. A checkbox is more user friendly than a drop down in that case. It also saves some space in the column of the table.\n2. Did you make sure SDC user gets proper a message, in case of leaving the window without saving changes?\n3. Can you make sure sdc-tosca parser can provide the required value of inputs?\n\nEventually, please run the CSIT locally to ensure all tests pass.\n\nThanks!",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
